L. S. FISHER et al., Appellants, v. Johanna Geertson KELLY, etc., et al., Appellees. No. 6411. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 16, 1931.

Before RUDKIN, WILBUR and SAW-TELLE, Cireuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to motion of appellees, ordered appeal dismissed for failure of appellants to file record and docket cause; mandate forthwith.
